01:05:34,300 --> 01:05:38,317
-Nice. And my hair didn't
even get messed up.

901
01:05:40,622 --> 01:05:42,854
-Who's chicken now?

902
01:05:45,071 --> 01:05:47,961
-This little piggy
kicked some alien butt.

903
01:05:47,961 --> 01:05:50,712
-Good one! Now my turn.

904
01:05:55,536 --> 01:05:57,774
-What? What?

905
01:05:57,774 --> 01:05:59,871
Why are you
all looking at me like that?

906
01:05:59,871 --> 01:06:03,061
Let me guess.
My hair got messed up.

907
01:06:03,061 --> 01:06:04,635
-Lizzie, don't freak out,

908
01:06:04,635 --> 01:06:07,782
but when you combination
sneeze-farted,
you got stuck mid-morph.

909
01:06:07,782 --> 01:06:10,225
-You can't show up for Mom's
meatloaf looking like that.

910
01:06:10,225 --> 01:06:13,367
-Brittany, stop!
We all know your mom's gone,
and you just eat chips.

911
01:06:13,367 --> 01:06:14,977
-I don't just eat chips.

912
01:06:14,977 --> 01:06:17,348
I eat chips...and soda.

913
01:06:17,348 --> 01:06:20,490
-Okay. Hey, we can
figure this out, guys.
Let's put our heads together.

914
01:06:20,490 --> 01:06:24,885
Oh, Lizzie, can you
just look at the wall
while we talk?
-Sure.

915
01:06:26,309 --> 01:06:30,018
-A little hard to see.
I'm kind of looking
in two directions at once.

916
01:06:30,018 --> 01:06:31,990
-Think, guys.
How can we fix this?

917
01:06:31,990 --> 01:06:36,831
-Okay, maybe if I sneeze
and then fart again,
I can change back.

918
01:06:38,509 --> 01:06:40,810
-Lizzie, stop.
You're gonna hurt yourself.

919
01:06:40,810 --> 01:06:45,153
-Maybe if I fart twice,
then sneeze once, then burp?

920
01:06:47,826 --> 01:06:50,011
-Yuck!
-That didn't work.

921
01:06:50,011 --> 01:06:53,580
Okay, what about,
um, sneeze, fart, pause,

922
01:06:53,580 --> 01:06:57,194
spin around,
fart three times quickly,
burp once, then fart again?

923
01:06:57,194 --> 01:07:00,234
-Definitely not.
Maybe if I do it?
-Yeah.

924
01:07:06,923 --> 01:07:09,293
-I have to go home.

925
01:07:15,545 --> 08:02:32,960
-Oh, no! Chumongous is coming!
It's time to morph back.

926
08:02:32,950 --> 08:02:35,750
-That's right! The great
Chumongous has returned.

927
08:02:35,760 --> 08:02:37,830
You Earth kids may have
thought you've defeated me,

928
08:02:37,820 --> 08:02:39,390
but I'm more powerful than ever!

929
08:02:39,390 --> 08:02:42,030
Oh, my God, it smells
like [bleep] in here.

930
08:02:42,030 --> 08:02:43,800
-Sorry. We've all been spinning,

931
08:02:43,800 --> 08:02:45,600
farting, and burping
for the past few minutes.

932
08:02:45,600 --> 08:02:48,070
-Why? Actually. Never mind.
I don't care.

933
08:02:48,070 --> 08:02:51,070
Prepare to die!

934
08:02:51,070 --> 08:02:52,240
You...

935
08:02:54,310 --> 08:02:56,510
...beautiful creature.

936
08:02:56,510 --> 08:02:59,980
You're just about the most
perfect thing I've ever seen.

937
08:02:59,980 --> 08:03:01,920
- You really think so?

938
08:03:01,910 --> 08:03:05,610
-Yes. There's just one problem.

939
08:03:05,620 --> 08:03:06,620
-What is it?

940
08:03:07,750 --> 08:03:11,020
-That frog hand
ain't got my thing in it.

941
08:03:11,020 --> 08:03:12,760
-Ew, dude!

942
08:03:12,760 --> 08:03:14,530
-Sorry. Is that, like,
a big deal for you guys?

943
08:03:14,530 --> 08:03:16,330
That's, like, less
than first base where I'm from.

944
08:03:16,330 --> 08:03:17,600
Where I'm from,

945
08:03:17,600 --> 08:03:18,900
if you go visit your grandmother
in the hospital,

946
08:03:18,900 --> 08:03:20,670
you lean over
and your grandma just

947
08:03:20,670 --> 08:03:23,440
grabs your thing out of respect!

948
08:03:23,440 --> 08:03:26,040
-What?
-So, what do you say?

949
08:03:26,040 --> 08:03:28,510
You want to be
my queen of Chumonga?

950
08:03:28,510 --> 08:03:32,150
-Well...it sure beats homework.

